lead_paragraph: Spaniard Dani Pedrosa plans to race in MotoGP's Valencia season-ender this weekend, a month after the Honda rider fractured his collarbone, leg and foot in a crash in Japan.

headline.print_headline: Pedrosa to Return for Valencia Season-Ender
headline.main: Pedrosa to Return for Valencia Season-Ender
